The folder contains the following data files:
1. gama-galaxies-7187.txt: data for 7,187 galaxies from the Galaxy And Mass Assembly (GAMA) survey, with redshifts in the range 0.05 < 𝑧 < 0.08.
2. gama-galaxies-enviro-7187.txt: environmental measurements associated with the above galaxy sample.

Data source:
The galaxy data consist of local-Universe galaxies from GAMA DR4 at https://gama-survey.org/dr4/data/cat. 
The galaxy features were obtained from the following GAMA DR4 tables: MagPhysv06, StellarMassesPanChromv24 (for rest-frame $u-r$ colour), and BDModelsv05. 
The environmental data consist of three local galaxy environment measures from the GAMA DR4 file server, EnvironmentMeasuresv06, https://gama-survey.org/dr4/data/cat/EnvironmentMeasures/v06/.
